val1.title: DNA EDA App | EC2, Streamlit, S3, FastAPI ,Pandas
project_desc: Takes a DNA Sequence Input for Nucleotide Composition of DNA
Does EDA on the Input System and shows distribution of ATGC count
Uses Pandas and Plotly for Data Analysis and Visualization

val2.title: Prescription Drug Knowledge | EC2, OpenAI, NLP, Streamlit
project_desc: Takes input a Drug Name as described in Prescription
Used Transformers based OpenAI API for Prediction
Predicts Description, Doctor Confirmation, Consumption Steps, Dosage

val3.title: Symptom Disorder Prediction | FB-bart, Transformer, NLP, EC2
project_desc: Takes Inputs Symptoms of a Patient with few Disorder Options
Predict the Probability of Disorder based on context of Symptoms
Uses Zero-Classification for prediction of Disorder from FB-BART model
